Install Docker plugins in jenkins.

Add the exec commad in doicker host.

Create docker file:
1) Insall open ssh in order to connect to the ubuntu container.
2)Install java packages over there.
3) Add jenkins user and change its password.
4) Expose ssh port 22.


Configure docker node as a cloud in jenkins.
add docker host url and test connection.
add docker agent template.-> Add your dockerhub imageurl.-> Connect with SSh -> Add your remote rrot dir.->Add ssh Credentials that you mentioned in docker file.

then create free style projects and add label and execute in shell.
